data.description: "Escape to picturesque West Brookfield! Nestled on 2.15 acres of scenic countryside, this 3-bed, 2.5-bath gem boasts 2002 sq. ft. of charm. The 1st floor offers a cabinet-packed kitchen with granite countertops w/ a nice island, a formal dining room, spacious front-to-back living room, and a 1/2 bath! On the 2nd floor you will find a sizable primary bedroom w/ a private bath and walk-in closet, 2 more good-sized bedrooms & the 2nd full bathroom! Finished bonus room on the 3rd floor! 2-car attached garage. Relax on your back deck and embrace the serenity of a private country setting. Your idyllic retreat awaits!" See the attached 3D Matterport video and floor plans!
